settings.testimonial_content_1: Love this product. Perfect for healthy snacking. Flavor is spot on and texture is better than the real thing.
settings.testimonial_content_2: My mouth is watering just typing this out.  This is the best "meaty" snack I have had in a long time.  The flavours are incredible.
settings.testimonial_content_3: I was amazed that mushrooms can be prepared and spiced in such a way as to resemble and taste like beef jerky
settings.testimonial_content_4: The flavor is rich, and delicious. A bit of a kick, but you can taste the sweetness as well! My non-vegan family members really like this one :)
settings.testimonial_content_5: Tastes better than real meat jerky and the flavor is amazing

settings.testimonial_content_1: I could describe them would be a replica beef teriyaki. My mouth is salivating writing this.
settings.testimonial_content_2: Every flavor is outstanding! Texture is spot on as well. Will buy again and again!
settings.testimonial_content_3: I also liked the fact that you were able to retain some softness in texture. Most Jerky products often are too tough, and harsh on the teeth. These were exceptional.
settings.testimonial_content_4: GREAT! The texture and taste are on point. Great substitute to meat. They're changing my husband's mind about mushrooms :)
settings.testimonial_content_5: These are great!  My husband thinks these are "spot on" flavor wise and the texture from the mushroom is as good as regular meat jerky.  We'll be getting these again
settings.testimonial_content_6: Love these - all three flavors. In between meals and just feel like snacking, Moku is the best. Great chew factor. Very satisfying

settings.testimonial_content_1: The texture is spot on and the flavors are better than beef jerky. This is my favorite snack!
settings.testimonial_content_2: Taste and texture of all three flavors was excellent! I’ve been eating it right out of the bag.
settings.testimonial_content_3: This snack is very tasty.  I love the flavor.  It is also great that the nutritional value is high without the high sodium content of meat jerky.
settings.testimonial_content_4: Chewy texture and great smoky flavor. I eat the entire bag in one sitting!
settings.testimonial_content_5: The flavors are so different/unique. What a surprise when my friends found out it wasn't meat but mushrooms!
settings.testimonial_content_6: YUM!  As a vegan, I am so happy to be able to enjoy a jerky that is healthful, better for our environment and cruelty-free.

settings.question: How much jerky is in a bag?
settings.answer: Each resealable bag has 2oz of jerky which is two servings. Each bag has 9g of fiber and 6g of protein. Mushroom jerky is also not as dense as beef jerky so we can fit a lot more pieces into a 2oz bag.

settings.question: What kind of mushrooms do you use?
settings.answer: We use King Oyster Mushrooms which are grown indoors on logs.  We do not use any chemicals or synthetic fertilizers when growing the mushrooms.

settings.question: How long will it take to receive my order?
settings.answer: We do our best to ship most orders on the next business day and then it takes 3-5 business days to be delivered.
